
'''''The Cursed Ones''''' ni filime yo mu Bwongereza ya 2015 yayobowe na Nana Obiri Yeboah ikorwa na Nicholas K. Lory . Amashusho yumwimerere yanditswe na Maximilian Claussen . Iyi filime ivuga amateka y’umunyamakuru wacitse intege ndetse n’umupasitori ukiri muto ufite ibitekerezo, urwanira kubohora umukobwa uregwa ubupfumu mu maboko ya gahunda yononekaye n’imiziririzo hagati muri Afurika y’iburengerazuba .

Filime yahawe ibihembo 3 bya African Movie Academy Awards mu 2016 ''kubuyobozi bwiza'', ''Sinema nziza'', hamwe nubushakashatsi ''bwiza'' .  Yatowe mu bihembo 13 bya AMAA byose hamwe, bituma iba filime yatowe kurusha izindi mu 2016. <ref>http://ama-awards.com/v/index.php/news/540-press-release-breaking-news-amaa-announces-2016-nomination-list</ref>

